@BorntraegerMarc you should be able to access this using TypeScript's [indexed access types](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/advanced-types.html#index-types):

``` ts
import { SessionOptions } from 'express-session';
type CookieOptions = SessionOptions['cookie'];
```

